data.comment: The match is underway at Gamla Ullevi.
Muamer Tankovic (Hammarby) goes close with a header but the ball is scrambled away by Goteborg defenders.
In the minute 1, Throw-in Hammarby.
Important block from the Goteborg defence as Paulinho fires in a strike for Hammarby.
Hammarby have been awarded a corner by Kristoffer Karlsson.
In the minute 2, Can Hammarby capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Goteborg's half?
Can Goteborg get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Hammarby's half?
Hammarby advance rapidly upfield but Kristoffer Karlsson blows for offside.
In the minute 6, Throw-in for Hammarby in the half of Goteborg.
Free kick for Goteborg in their own half.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
In the minute 12, Kristoffer Karlsson awards the home team a throw-in.
Kristoffer Karlsson signals a free kick to Goteborg in their own half.
Ball goes out of play for a Hammarby goal kick.
In the minute 15, Hammarby are too eager and fall into an offside trap.
Hammarby drive upfield and Paulinho gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Goteborg defender.
Hammarby are coming forward and Aron Johannsson gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
In the minute 19, Kristoffer Karlsson awards Goteborg a goal kick.
Goal! Aron Johannsson gives Hammarby a 0-1 lead in Gothenburg.
Throw-in high up the field for Hammarby in Gothenburg.
In the minute 22, It's a goal kick for the home team in Gothenburg.
Free kick for Goteborg in the half of Hammarby.
Throw-in for Hammarby in their own half.
In the minute 25, Ball safe as Goteborg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Kristoffer Karlsson signals a Hammarby throw-in in Goteborg's half.
Corner awarded to Hammarby.
In the minute 26, Hammarby push forward at Gamla Ullevi and Darijan Bojanic gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Goteborg defence.
Goteborg awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Hammarby have a goal kick.
In the minute 31, Paulinho for the away team is judged to be offside.
At Gamla Ullevi, Mads Fenger has been yellow-carded for the away team.
Kristoffer Karlsson signals a free kick to Goteborg.
In the minute 32, Hammarby to take a throw-in in Goteborg territory.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Goteborg will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Hammarby.
In the minute 38, Hammarby's Paulinho misses with an attempt on goal.
Goal kick for Goteborg at Gamla Ullevi.
Goteborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 40, Goteborg to take a throw-in in Hammarby territory.
Free kick for Goteborg in their own half.
Goteborg's Christian Kouakou has been booked in Gothenburg.
In the minute 44, Corner awarded to Goteborg.
Kristoffer Karlsson blows against Goteborg's Christian Kouakou for offside.
At Gamla Ullevi the fourth official shows that 2 minutes will be added to the 1st half.
In Gothenburg, Goteborg push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
In the minute 45, Throw-in for Goteborg at Gamla Ullevi.
Kristoffer Karlsson signals a free kick to Goteborg in their own half.
Kristoffer Karlsson blows to end the first-half.
In the minute 45, The match has been stopped briefly for attention to the injured Darijan Bojanic.
It seems as if Darijan Bojanic is unable to continue. Aimar Sher replaces him for the away team.
In the minute 46, The second-half is underway at Gamla Ullevi.
Pontus Wernbloom is on a sub for Christian Kouakou for Goteborg.
Alexander Farnerud is replacing Yahya Kalley for the home team.
In the minute 47, Goteborg have been awarded a corner by Kristoffer Karlsson.
Hammarby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Goteborg push upfield and Patrik Karlsson Lagemyr gets his head to the ball. The attempt is cleared by an alert Hammarby defence.
In the minute 49, In Gothenburg Hammarby attack through Paulinho. The finish is off target, however.
Goal kick for Goteborg at Gamla Ullevi.
Can Hammarby get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Goteborg's half?
In the minute 51, Kristoffer Karlsson awards the home team a throw-in.
Free kick for Goteborg in their own half.
Ball safe as Goteborg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 53, Goteborg push upfield but Kristoffer Karlsson quickly pulls them for offside.
Goteborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
Jeppe Andersen (Hammarby) has received a yellow card from Kristoffer Karlsson.
In the minute 55, Throw-in for Hammarby at Gamla Ullevi.
In Gothenburg, Paulinho (Hammarby) misses the target with a header.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Gothenburg.
In the minute 57, Throw-in for Hammarby in the half of Goteborg.
Ball goes out of play for a Goteborg goal kick.
Hammarby have a goal kick.
Kristoffer Karlsson signals a free kick to Hammarby in their own half.
In the minute 59, Pontus Wernbloom (Goteborg) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
Hammarby have a dangerous throw-in.
In the minute 60, Free kick for Goteborg in their own half.
Aimar Sher for Hammarby has been booked by Kristoffer Karlsson and receives a first yellow card.
Abdul Khalili (Hammarby) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 66, Goteborg awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Kristoffer Karlsson signals a free kick to Hammarby in their own half.
Hammarby needs to be cautious. Goteborg have an attacking throw-in.
Corner awarded to Hammarby.
In the minute 71, The away team replace Aron Johannsson with Gustav Ludwigson.
Ferran Sibila Pont is making the team's third substitution at Gamla Ullevi with Giorgi Kharaishvili replacing Patrik Karlsson Lagemyr.
In the minute 72, Great finish from Muamer Tankovic to give Hammarby a 0-2 lead.
That's a fine assist from Gustav Ludwigson.
Hammarby's Gustav Ludwigson gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 73, Kristoffer Karlsson awards Goteborg a goal kick.
Hammarby awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 75, Free kick for Goteborg in their own half.
Hammarby's Mohanad Jeahze has been booked in Gothenburg.
Throw-in for Goteborg close to the penalty box.
Goal kick for Hammarby at Gamla Ullevi.
In the minute 78, Throw-in Goteborg.
Goal! Muamer Tankovic extends Hammarby's lead to 0-3.
Gustav Ludwigson instrumental with a fine assist.
In the minute 80, Kristoffer Karlsson signals a Goteborg throw-in in Hammarby's half.
Goteborg have been awarded a corner by Kristoffer Karlsson.
Jakob Johansson (Goteborg) wins the ball in the air but heads wide.
In the minute 81, Hammarby have a goal kick.
At Gamla Ullevi, Hammarby are penalized for being offside.
In Gothenburg a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 84, Free kick Hammarby.
Goteborg make their fourth substitution with Jesper Tolinsson replacing Jakob Johansson.
The home team have replaced Alhassan Yusuf with Sargon Abraham. This is the fifth substitution made today by Ferran Sibila Pont.
In the minute 85, Goteborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Throw-in for Goteborg in the half of Hammarby.
In the minute 87, Goal! Hammarby extend their lead to 0-4 through Muamer Tankovic.
Great play from Gustav Ludwigson to set up the goal.
Stefan Billborn (Hammarby) is making a third substitution, with Imad Khalili replacing Jeppe Andersen.
In the minute 88, Simon Sandberg is on a sub for Tim Soderstrom for Hammarby.
Ball goes out of play for a Hammarby goal kick.
In Gothenburg a free kick has been awarded the away team.
The fourth official's board shows 3 minutes, which will be added to the 2nd half.
Kristoffer Karlsson signals a free kick to Hammarby in their own half.
Can Goteborg capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
Kristoffer Karlsson awards Hammarby a goal kick.
The match is over. Final score 0-4.
